<lyrics>[V1]
 1- yạ ḥbyby rạỷʿ ḥbk nḥw hạlk
 nẓyry yạ ḥbyby
 gẖạrq fy ạlạ̹tẖm ạ̉hwy̱ fy ạlẓlạm dẖạ mṣyry
 ạ̉rzḥ fy qyd sẖry fy mrạr kạlạ̉syr
 fạ̉tyt wfdyt wgẖlbt yạ qdyr
 wạqfaⁿạ fy ạltẖgẖr wḥdk nṣyry yạ ḥbyby
 2- yạ ḥbyby rạỷʿ ḥbk rạỷʿ ḥbk nḥw kl
 ạlậtẖmyn
 ạ̹dẖ mạzlt tdʿw trjw qlb qạs ky ylyn
 bạlmḥbẗ tnạdy ạqblwạ yạ mtʿbyn
 ạ̉ḥml ạlạ̉tẖqạl ʿnkm ạ̉frḥ ạlqlb ạlḥzyn
 yạ lrwʿẗ kẖlạṣk ạltẖmyn yạ ḥbyby</lyrics>
<title>rạỷʿ ḥbk</title>
